   *Components* V, S, M (a handful of clay, crystal, or glass spheres)

   *Range*medium (100 ft. + 10 ft./level)

   *Target* one creature

   *Duration* instantaneous

   *Saving Throw*[Will] negates; see text; **note Spell Resistance:
