5 feet). If you are within 200 feet and speak a word of command, each
berry instantly bursts into flame, causing 1d8 points of fire damage +
1 point per caster level to every creature in a 5-foot-radius burst and
igniting any combustible materials within 5 feet. A creature in the
area that makes a successful [Reflex] saving throw takes only half
damage.

