30 Types of Feats
*****************

Some feats are general, meaning that no special rules govern them as a
group. Others are item creation feats, which allow characters to create
magic items of all sorts. A metamagic feat lets a spellcaster prepare
and cast a spell with greater effect, albeit as if the spell were of a
higher spell level than it actually is.

