30.2 Critical Feats
===================

Critical feats modify the effects of a critical hit by inflicting an
additional condition on the victim of the critical hit. Characters
without the Critical Mastery feat can only apply the effects of one
critical feat to an individual critical hit. Characters with multiple
critical feats can decide which feat to apply after the critical hit
has been confirmed.


