31.1 Acrobatic
==============

You are skilled at leaping, jumping, and flying.

   *Benefit:* You get a +2 bonus on all *note Acrobatics: #acrobatics.
and *note Fly: #fly. skill checks. If you have 10 or more ranks in one
of these skills, the bonus increases to +4 for that skill.


