31.3 Agile Maneuvers (Combat)
=============================

You've learned to use your quickness in place of brute force when
performing combat maneuvers.

   *Benefit:* You add your [Dexterity] bonus to your base attack bonus
and size bonus when determining your [Combat Maneuver Bonus] (see
[Combat]) instead of your Strength bonus.

   *Normal:* You add your Strength bonus to your base attack bonus and
size bonus when determining your [Combat Maneuver Bonus].


