31.4 Alertness
==============

You often notice things that others might miss.

   *Benefit:* You get a +2 bonus on *note Perception: #perception. and
*note Sense Motive: #sense-motive. skill checks. If you have 10 or more
ranks in one of these skills, the bonus increases to +4 for that skill.


