shadowdancer gains a special ability that allows her to confound her
foes. This functions as the [rogue talent] class feature. A
shadowdancer cannot select an individual talent more than once. If a
shadowdancer has the [advanced talents] rogue class feature, she can
chose from the [advanced talents] list instead.

