shadow, an undead shade. Unlike a normal shadow, this shadow's
alignment matches that of the shadowdancer, and the creature cannot
create spawn. The summoned shadow receives a +4 bonus on [Will] saves
made to halve the damage from positive channeled energy and the shadow
cannot be turned or commanded. This shadow serves as a companion to the
shadowdancer and can communicate intelligibly with the shadowdancer.
