total of 40 feet each day in this way; this may be a single jump of 40
feet or four jumps of 10 feet each. Every two levels higher than 4th,
the distance a shadowdancer can jump each day doubles (80 feet at 6th,
160 feet at 8th, and 320 feet at 10th). This amount can be split among
